Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.88,Default,Shinichirou,0000,0000,0000,,Ai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.95,Default,Shinichirou,0000,0000,0000,,Chờ đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:27.72,Default,Aiko,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.08,Default,Shinichirou,0000,0000,0000,,Ai-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.04,Default,Aiko,0000,0000,0000,,Làm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:58.33,Default,Aiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hãy để ý đến chị nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:01.73,Default,Aiko,0000,0000,0000,,Làm ơn mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.64,Default,Aiko,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichirou...
